# RFMpackage

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of RFMpackage is to calculate weighted RFM scores based on recency, frequency and monetary values of customer purchases and sort customers to groups

## Installation

You can install the released version of RFMpackage from github

